  <brief_title>FET-PET for Diagnosis and Monitoring in Patients With Low Grade Glioma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Molecular Correlates and Clinical Significance of Positron Emission Tomography With FET-PET in Combination With Perfusion-weighted Magnetic Resonance Imaging (PWI) in Patients With Low Grade Gliomas</official_title>
